{"type": "article", "id": 25595, "title": "螺旋腿边桌", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-18T07:08:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 18, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607130040XzwIfomYMxGeAW8O.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是 Nendo 为意大利品牌 Capellini 设计的白色边桌，是用铁做的，一共三种型号。中间型号的桌子是最基本的形状，另外两张桌子都带有一根螺旋形状的弯曲桌腿，使桌子之间构成环环相扣的状态。可以沿着桌腿将另一张桌子旋转出来，当不需要使用时又收回去。螺旋形的设计并不复杂，倒是给人一种奇妙的趣味。<a href=\"http://www.nendo.jp/en/works/tangle-table-3/?erelease\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130037Ji640OSBmafl7IVY.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70731707\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130038zv4DZsBxkGcyfEp3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130038SaWHArkYgBwDqtEm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130039fQM6KcpDU5HnZRyX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89209402\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px; height: 268px; width: 375px; left: 533px; top: 1329px;\" class=\"dragged\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071300394xhmnj2zL7OflVkJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607130040QPXGwBtRzlf3Ogi7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.71388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}